    "asOf": "2022-08-30",
    "date": "2022-10-11T14:26:20Z",
    "text": "Restoring Workers' Rights Act of 2022\n\nThis bill prohibits an employer from enforcing, or threatening to enforce, any non-compete agreement in employment contracts. This prohibition does not apply to employees who are exempt from federal overtime pay requirements. A non-compete agreement entered into before the enactment of this bill shall be void and have no effect."
